msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"If Sakura died from Hiro's single blow, that doesn't\n"
"explain why she had <CLT 3>two head wounds<CLT>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Huh? Two...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "That's right. She had two separate wounds on her head."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"And remember, this girl examines dead bodies as a\n"
"hobby. Personally, I'm inclined to believe her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"But...I only hit her <CLT 3>once<CLT>. How could she have <CLT 3>two<CLT>\n"
"wounds?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"Two wounds means she was <CLT 3>struck twice<CLT>. What's more,\n"
"both attacks must have come from a Monokuma Bottle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"H-Hold on! How can you know that j-just from some cuts\n"
"on her head?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid "She was a-attacked twice! With two M-Monokuma Bottles!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"It's not just because of her head wounds. It's also\n"
"because of the Monokuma Bottles themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"There's something <CLT 3>very suspicious<CLT> about those\n"
"bottles..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"Once you understand that point, you'll understand why\n"
"two separate Monokuma Bottles must have been used."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"Think back...after the incident, there were <CLT 3>4\n"
"Monokuma Bottles<CLT> left on the shelf, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"And we found pieces of a bottle on the ground, along\n"
"with the chess piece it had inside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "That was the bottle Hiro hit Sakura with, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"For now, just note that there were four intact\n"
"bottles, and one broken bottle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"But originally, there were <CLT 3>six<CLT> bottles in total.\n"
"Meaning one has gone missing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid ""
"But h-how can you know for sure there were s-six\n"
"bottles...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid "That's easy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"If you look at what the bottles <CLT 3>all had in common<CLT>,\n"
"it should become clear."
msgstr ""
